Returns a time series representing pumped volume at a well or series of wells, summed daily for a given date range.
Each point in the output time series represents the total pumped volume for the given day.
get.description:
Sample requests:
            
    Returns data for ALL wells from 8/1/2021 to 8/31/2021
    GET /api/wells/pumpedVolume?startDate=2021-08-01&endDate=2021-08-31
            
    Returns data for Well Registration IDs G-056157, G-097457, G-110920 from 8/1/2021 to 8/31/2021
    GET /api/wells/pumpedVolume?startDate=2021-08-01&endDate=2021-08-31&wellRegistrationID=G-056157&wellRegistrationID=G-097457&wellRegistrationID=G-110920

parameters.name: wellRegistrationID
parameters.description: The Well Registration ID(s) for the requested Well(s). If left blank, will bring back data for every Well that has reported data within the time range.

parameters.name: startDate
parameters.description: The start date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)

parameters.name: endDate
parameters.description: The end date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)

Each point in the output time series represents the total pumped volume for the given day.

parameters.name: wellRegistrationID
parameters.description: The Well Registration ID for the requested Well.

parameters.name: startDate
parameters.description: The start date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)

parameters.name: endDate
parameters.description: The end date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)

put.summary: Migrates Influx records associated with the specified Well Pressure sensor from the first specified well to the second.

parameters.name: sensorName
parameters.description: The device number for the sensor readings to be migrated.

parameters.name: fromWellRegistrationID
parameters.description: The registration ID for the well which the specified sensor readings should be migrated from.

parameters.name: toWellRegistrationID
parameters.description: The registration ID for the well which the specified sensor readings should be migrated to.

parameters.name: bucket
parameters.description: The bucket to be used for the Influx operations.

parameters.name: startDate
parameters.description: The start date for the readings to be migrated in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2022-06-23). If no date is provided, 2018-01-01 will be used by default.

parameters.name: endDate
parameters.description: The end date for the readings to be migrated in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2022-07-01). If no date is provided, the current date will be used by default.
